title: Roe vs Wade Ended, David Dobrik Hires Johnny Depp's Lawyer - After Dark #75
description: Today we discuss the utterly tragic news regarding Roe vs Wade. We also find some energy after such a heavy topic to celebrate Ethan's birthday with a special surprise, a potential defamation lawsuit from David Dobrik incoming, the Bored Apes creator contacts us to clear their name, and much more!
